561
00:36:43,000 --> 00:36:44,660
We'll see Uncle off together.

562
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:49,160
If he can see us,

563
00:36:51,640 --> 00:36:53,300
he will surely leave in peace.

564
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,160
Minmin,

565
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:39,440
I've always wanted to ask Father

566
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:43,370
when he took up his post years ago,

567
00:37:45,790 --> 00:37:48,400
why did he take
only Ming Chu and her mother

568
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:55,720
and leave me behind
in this mansion?

569
00:37:58,080 --> 00:37:59,360
All these years,

570
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:02,160
I've carefully managed the household,

571
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:06,080
building a name
and reputation for us in the capital.

572
00:38:08,130 --> 00:38:09,600
In the end,

573
00:38:11,340 --> 00:38:13,680
it was all to win Father's approval,

574
00:38:15,520 --> 00:38:19,640
to be closer to him.

575
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:23,520
For five long years,

576
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:26,140
I wished every day for his return.

577
00:38:27,490 --> 00:38:30,880
But when I finally saw him again,

578
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,200
though my heart was full of words,

579
00:38:36,330 --> 00:38:38,640
I didn't know where to begin.

580
00:38:40,680 --> 00:38:44,400
I thought we still had time,

581
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,520
plenty of time

582
00:38:48,270 --> 00:38:50,360
for me to be a filial daughter,

583
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:53,720
to make up for the distance

584
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:56,600
and regret

585
00:38:56,600 --> 00:38:58,200
between us.

586
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:02,840
But how could I have known

587
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:07,560
that in the span of a single day,

588
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:12,720
death would separate us forever?

589
00:39:33,880 --> 00:39:34,840
Your Highness,

590
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:38,680
though I never met the Marquis,

591
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:41,440
I believe that when he brought

592
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:43,160
your sister along,

593
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:45,240
it wasn't out of favoritism.

594
00:39:48,640 --> 00:39:51,840
Yun Yi, how would you know that?

595
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:16,280
His Highness told me.

596
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,920
Before the Marquis left,

597
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,360
he met with His Highness.

598
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:21,400
He didn't wish to see you

599
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:24,080
because he feared it would

600
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:25,610
only bring you more sorrow.

601
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:27,360
He said

602
00:40:27,840 --> 00:40:30,880
parting in life
is better than farewell in death.

603
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:33,840
He begged His Highness again and again

604
00:40:33,860 --> 00:40:35,160
to protect you,

605
00:40:36,040 --> 00:40:37,680
to help you let go of the pain

606
00:40:38,600 --> 00:40:39,600
and recover soon.

607
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:42,960
What else did Father say?

608
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:45,960
The Marquis also said...

609
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:49,480
“When I set off for Yangxi Prefecture,

610
00:40:50,160 --> 00:40:52,160
I feared I'd be gone for many years.

611
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:56,600
If I left Liu and her daughter behind,
they might make things hard for Tan.

612
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:58,440
And the southern frontier
was often at war,

613
00:40:58,440 --> 00:41:00,170
the people living in hardship.

614
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,680
If I brought her,

615
00:41:03,680 --> 00:41:05,200
she'd suffer too.

616
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,400
So after much thought,

617
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:13,400
I decided to take Liu and her daughter

618
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:14,840
with me.

619
00:41:17,080 --> 00:41:18,940
Tan lost her mother at a young age.

620
00:41:20,270 --> 00:41:22,640
I already owed her too much.

621
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:27,520
How could I let her suffer again
by taking her to the borderlands?

622
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,720
But ever since then,

623
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,600
whenever I left home,

624
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:36,240
Tan never came to see me off again.

625
00:41:40,600 --> 00:41:42,240
She must

626
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:46,920
have felt hurt,

627
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:51,440
and blamed me.”

628
00:42:58,080 --> 00:43:03,840
♪ It's a journey full of ups and downs ♪

629
00:43:00,180 --> 00:43:02,440
Your Highness, you should get some rest.

630
00:43:02,680 --> 00:43:04,010
I'll stay and keep watch

631
00:43:04,480 --> 00:43:05,600
with Her Highness.

632
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:11,540
♪ It's a journey full of coldness ♪

633
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:11,660
Ask the kitchen

634
00:43:12,680 --> 00:43:13,640
to prepare bird's nest porridge.

635
00:43:13,640 --> 00:43:16,320
♪ The wind combs through my hair ♪

636
00:43:15,240 --> 00:43:15,960
and Tan's

637
00:43:15,960 --> 00:43:17,320
favorite snacks.

638
00:43:17,270 --> 00:43:20,710
♪ Putting pen to paper, I write about our past ♪

639
00:43:18,480 --> 00:43:19,880
Bring these over

640
00:43:20,560 --> 00:43:21,800
whenever Tan feels like eating them.

641
00:43:21,690 --> 00:43:25,090
♪ Tears on the face, pain in the heart ♪

642
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:22,800
Yes.

643
00:43:28,430 --> 00:43:34,530
♪ Looking back, what a long road filled with uncertainties ♪

644
00:43:36,040 --> 00:43:42,190
♪ Who to share
the wavering candle light with? ♪

