00:43:44,350 --> 00:43:47,040
♪ Words are cold ♪

646
00:43:48,090 --> 00:43:50,650
♪ I always remember the promise
to get old with you ♪

647
00:43:51,280 --> 00:43:56,070
♪ Sigh! Vows are like snowflakes
resting on my palm ♪

648
00:43:57,070 --> 00:44:01,240
♪ The vicissitudes of life never cease ♪

649
00:44:01,940 --> 00:44:05,360
♪ You and I are looking for the truth ♪

